ирайте из широкого набора разделителей фигур и разделяйте свои разделы бесконечными способами, которые до сих пор были просто невозможны.</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:14585:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gguex\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ff963c9a361b65e2420cab6161e935fd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ff963c9a361b65e2420cab6161e935fd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gguex\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Georges Guex <small>(gguex)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">17 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">La Classe</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Bloated s**t</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gazdik\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/80adde83b60681bf2d172c80be7609f7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/80adde83b60681bf2d172c80be7609f7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gazdik\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gazdik</a> <span class=\"review-date\">16 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is bloated with DIVs. Slow and they are adding really not useful features for developers and agencies. Only small shiny object things like PayPal button. I mean are you kidding me? Terrible and I am disappointed. I will be canceling my subscription and moving to Oxygen.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Update Broke Everything</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lastauka\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee5987d44796a797e2a1d5f873ad914d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee5987d44796a797e2a1d5f873ad914d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lastauka\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lastauka</a> <span class=\"review-date\">15 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I was extremely hesitant to download the update on my main website and made a side website specifically to test if it would work with all of the other plugins I need. Unlike some of the other recent reviews that say simply some margins, etc, are out of wack, my entire website is unable to be updated. Every page requires Elementor to be updated and absolutely none of them are working. I\'ve tried uninstalling and reinstalling everything under the sun and even stripping everything down to the base essential plugins. Elementor never actually loads on any of my pages. (Using GeneratePress Premium for anyone curious.) Whatever is in this new update has completely broken everything. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Always Excellent</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/slimtall\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3c4add52f9f45a85abf7c95348466ca?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3c4add52f9f45a85abf7c95348466ca?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/slimtall\" class=\"reviewer-name\">slimtall</a> <span class=\"review-date\">12 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Just love Elementor. All kind of customization\'s with WordPress web sites/blogs. They continue to add more awesome features. Pro version is great. Still learning new things with it :)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best page builder</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bystrikkralovic\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6dcf0623f8d5f084477ce5cd1b37ff83?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6dcf0623f8d5f084477ce5cd1b37ff83?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bystrikkralovic\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Bystrík Královič <small>(bystrikkralovic)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">12 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">They don\'t lie when they advertise Elementor as a \"The #1 Page Builder\".</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">:(</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/houstonbroker\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/09c6bd96c8f7da0379bfcf26631565d6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/09c6bd96c8f7da0379bfcf26631565d6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/houstonbroker\" class=\"reviewer-name\">houstonbroker</a> <span class=\"review-date\">16 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have a problem with the update. Elementor has a conflict with WP Multilingual Plugin, the page wouldn\'t load</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Intrusive: Your License Has Expired</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/frank4515\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/724053f715b97d71571947342df73a43?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/724053f715b97d71571947342df73a43?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/frank4515\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Frank Mendoza <small>(frank4515)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">10 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Me parece un plugin intrusivo, que si bien ha vencido la licencia PRO, esté invadiendo todo el panel de wordpress con ese recordatorio. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Pro Version Over-Priced</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/evildoer\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/feb94a59bd602553750067a69df45147?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/feb94a59bd602553750067a69df45147?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/evildoer\" class=\"reviewer-name\">evildoer</a> <span class=\"review-date\">9 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I would like to purchase the pro version - but the pricing is that of a complete custom theme ! \n\nI can do everything the pro version does with elementor add-ons.\n\nBut cut the price in half - where it should be - and I would sign up for the pro version in a heart beat.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Last Update broke all my templates</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/elk3rry\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8249e07a8e24594bc03382d44f2aeb07?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8249e07a8e24594bc03382d44f2aeb07?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/elk3rry\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Pedro Martinez Saro <small>(elk3rry)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">8 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Can\'t understand how these guys think of updates. Every single time an update comes out there is a problem. This time all of my templates are useless because of the margins, heights, or widths. Can\'t wait to drop Elementor for something better like Oxygen.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best in class . . .</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atudemi\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/726cb1d00ec11addfc29d03638a0d908?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/726cb1d00ec11addfc29d03638a0d908?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atudemi\" class=\"reviewer-name\">atudemi</a> <span class=\"review-date\">8 июня, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">. . . and easy to use.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.3.2.5.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:256:\"<strong>Перетащите и падения.</strong> Наше мгновенное сопротивление и падение позволяет легко поместить каждый элемент в любом месте на странице.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:284:\"<strong>Визуальный контроль размера.</strong> Настройте различные элементы страницы. Изменение размеров изображений, изменение размеров колонок и многое другое.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src