(817, 1, '2021-06-19 11:53:38', '2021-06-19 08:53:38', '', 'Wind of Freedom', 'This lightweight stalker bodysuit is made by Freedom craftsmen. The suit\'s fabric is treated with Horizon, a special solution developed by the faction by trial and error to increase resistance to anomalies. Like the Sunrise suit, the Wind of Freedom comes with built-in body armor and artifact containers.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'wind-of-freedom', '', '', '2021-06-19 11:53:43', '2021-06-19 08:53:43', '', 0, 'http://clearskyshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=817', 0, 'product', '', 0),
