(819, 1, '2021-06-19 11:55:36', '2021-06-19 08:55:36', '', 'SEVA suit', 'This bodysuit, intended for researching the Zone, combines a closed-cycle respiratory module and an external isolation coating, resulting in excellent protection from anomalies. Due to poor protection from physical impact, the suit is not a good defense against bullet and fragmentation damage. It comes with a built-in artifact transportation container.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'seva-suit', '', '', '2021-06-19 11:55:41', '2021-06-19 08:55:41', '', 0, 'http://clearskyshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=819', 0, 'product', '', 0),
