(821, 1, '2021-06-19 11:57:19', '2021-06-19 08:57:19', '', 'Guardian of Freedom suit', 'This stalker bodysuit with reinforced body armor made by Freedom craftsmen represents a good compromise between combat and anomaly protection. The built-in body armor comprises armor plating and ten Kevlar layers, capable of stopping a pistol bullet. The suit uses the relatively expensive Sovereign compound for anomaly protection. Comes with an artifact container.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'guardian-of-freedom-suit', '', '', '2021-06-19 11:57:24', '2021-06-19 08:57:24', '', 0, 'http://clearskyshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=821', 0, 'product', '', 0),
