(823, 1, '2021-06-19 11:59:55', '2021-06-19 08:59:55', '', 'PSZ-9d', 'This early model of the Duty bodysuit is the Spetsnaz PSZ-9 body armor modified for the Zone. The suit is capable of stopping a rifle bullet. However, this level of protection comes at the cost of its weight, bulkiness, and virtually non-existent anomaly protection. The suit cannot be modified with an artifact container but may be upgraded with a combat support system.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'psz-9d', '', '', '2021-06-19 12:00:00', '2021-06-19 09:00:00', '', 0, 'http://clearskyshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=823', 0, 'product', '', 0),
